OL,3,CElectrical fire shuts down Hawick
OL,5,FAn electrical fire caused an access
OL,6,Fpanel to explode in Hawick on Sunday
OL,7,Fmorning causing a widespread power-cut
OL,8,Facross the town.
OL,10,F, the Scottish Fire and Rescue
OL,11,FService, and Scottish Power attended
OL,12,Fthe scene on Commercial Road and the
OL,13,Fkey route through the town was shut
OL,14,Fand traffic diverted.
OL,16,FPower was quickly restored to many
OL,17,Fhomes and businesses, and the road was
OL,18,Fclosed for two hours for the emergency
OL,19,Fservices.
