OL,3,CElectrical fire shuts down Hawick
OL,5,FA bystander told ITV Border that it
OL,6,Fwas reported by someone posting a
OL,7,Fletter who 'got a fright' when the
OL,8,Faccess panel exploded. There are no
OL,9,Freports of any injuries.
OL,11,FA Police Scotland statement said:
OL,12,F"Officers assisted SFRS with a road
OL,13,Fclosure following a report of an
OL,14,Felectrical fault on Commercial Road, .
OL,15,FUtility company is at the scene and
OL,16,Fthe road is now open."
