OL,3,CElectrical fire shuts down Hawick
OL,5,FA Scottish Fire and Rescue statement
OL,6,Fsaid: "We were alerted at 10.58am on
OL,7,FSunday, 4 February to reports of
OL,8,Fflames from a manhole on a pavement on
OL,9,FCommercial Road, Hawick.
OL,11,F"Operations Control mobilised one
OL,12,Fappliance to extinguish the fire and
OL,13,Fassist partners in making the area
OL,14,Fsafe.
OL,16,F"Firefighters checked nearby
OL,17,Fcommercial and residential properties
OL,18,Fbut found no trace of smoke, fire or
OL,19,Fdamage. There were no reported
OL,20,Fcasualties and firefighters are no
OL,21,Flonger in attendance."
