OL,3,CElectrical fire shuts down Hawick
OL,5,FA spokesperson for SP Energy Networks
OL,6,Fsaid: "We apologise for any
OL,7,Finconvenience. A cable fault
OL,8,Ftemporarily interrupted the power
OL,9,Fsupply to around 9000 customers.
OL,11,F"Our engineers attended to swiftly and
OL,12,Fsafely restore the supply, with the
OL,13,Fmajority of customers back on within
OL,14,F10 minutes."
